channel.title: Whats the Newest
channel.description:
I was wondering to myself. "I wonder if there is a newer cheat client than the one im using?"
And so me and my nubby-ness are here to ask everyone of moparscape, if there is a newer cheat client than Azn or Bombs.
since Azn has so little features and Bombs refuses to work for me :)
So if there is a newer one please Tell me or Post a Link Thanks!
